headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: VeriSign (NASDAQ:VRSN) And The Rest Of The E-commerce Software Stocks
summary: As the Q4 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the e-commerce software industry, including VeriSign (NASDAQ:VRSN) and its peers.

headline: Warren Buffett Isn't Buying His Favorite Stock, but He's Been Scooping Up Shares of 3 Value Stocks Since 2025 Began
summary: Despite spending a cumulative $78 billion buying shares of his favorite stock since mid-2018, the Oracle of Omaha's attention is currently with three other holdings.
